Keep it up!\""},{"lineNumber":19948,"originalJapaneseLine":"「酒！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"More booze!\""},{"lineNumber":19949,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスは剣を手にぶら下げたまま、","translatedEnglishLine":"Lance, still holding his sword loosely,"},{"lineNumber":19950,"originalJapaneseLine":"コップを突き出す。","translatedEnglishLine":"held out his cup."},{"lineNumber":19951,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はいはい、ぞうどぞうど！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Alright, alright, here you go, here you go!"},{"lineNumber":19952,"originalJapaneseLine":"　どんどんいきましょーーーー」","translatedEnglishLine":"Let’s keep it goingoooo!\""},{"lineNumber":19953,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぐびぐびがぶがぶ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Glug glug, gulp gulp!\""},

{"lineNumber":19954,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うわはははははははは！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Uwahahahahaha!\""},

{"lineNumber":19955,"originalJapaneseLine":"「娘がーーーーーー！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"My daughterーーー!"},

{"lineNumber":19956,"originalJapaneseLine":"　好きだーーーーーーーーー！！","translatedEnglishLine":"I love herーーーーーー！！"},

{"lineNumber":19957,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ラヴーーーーーーーーー！！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Loveーーーーーー！！\""},

{"lineNumber":19958,"originalJapaneseLine":"「むう……なかなかはっきり物を言うじゃないか……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm... you speak quite clearly after all..."},

{"lineNumber":19959,"originalJapaneseLine":"　男らしい……ヤツだな！」","translatedEnglishLine":"You're a manly guy... indeed!\""},

{"lineNumber":19960,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なになになに！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What what what!"},

{"lineNumber":19961,"originalJapaneseLine":"　総統閣下ならそれ以上でしょう！　でしょう！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"If it's the Commander, it must be even more so! Right!?"},

{"lineNumber":19962,"originalJapaneseLine":"「むっ……むぬぬぬぬ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm... Munnnn!"},

{"lineNumber":19963,"originalJapaneseLine":"　あたりまえだろーーーーー！","translatedEnglishLine":"Of courseーーー!"},

{"lineNumber":19964,"originalJapaneseLine":"　俺様は……総統様だぞーーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I am... the Commanderーーー!\""},

{"lineNumber":19965,"originalJapaneseLine":"すぅっ、とランスは大きく息を吸った。","translatedEnglishLine":"Lance took a deep breath."},

{"lineNumber":19966,"originalJapaneseLine":"「………………………………………………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\".............................................\""},

{"lineNumber":19967,"originalJapaneseLine":"……ところで。","translatedEnglishLine":"...By the way."},

{"lineNumber":19968,"originalJapaneseLine":"シベリアより冷たい視線に気づいた。","translatedEnglishLine":"He noticed a gaze colder than Siberia."},

{"lineNumber":19969,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……………………あ゛？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...............Huh?\" "},

{"lineNumber":19970,"originalJapaneseLine":"「どうした。言うてみい。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What's wrong? Go ahead and say it."},

{"lineNumber":19971,"originalJapaneseLine":"　娘がどうと？」","translatedEnglishLine":"What about your daughter?\""},

{"lineNumber":19972,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さささ、言うがよい。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Go on, say it."},

{"lineNumber":19973,"originalJapaneseLine":"　この醜態、全て包み隠さず","translatedEnglishLine":"All of this disgrace, without hiding a thing,"},

{"lineNumber":19974,"originalJapaneseLine":"　リセットに伝えるからのう」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll tell Reset everything, you know.\" "},

{"lineNumber":19975,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ……………………あ、ぁ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah... ah...\" "},

{"lineNumber":19976,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おりょーん？　どうしたんですか、閣下！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh? What's wrong, Commander!"},

{"lineNumber":19977,"originalJapaneseLine":"　嫁さんですか？","translatedEnglishLine":"Is it your wife?"},

{"lineNumber":19978,"originalJapaneseLine":"　気にせずズバーっといきましょうよ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Don't worry, just go ahead and say it clearly!\""},

{"lineNumber":19979,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だ………………黙りゃれえええええ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Shut... up!!\""},

{"lineNumber":19980,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぎょふうううううっっ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gyofooooo!!\""},{"lineNumber":19981,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あっ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah!\""},{"lineNumber":19982,"originalJapaneseLine":"ビヨンホウはズバーッと斬られた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Biyonhou was slashed cleanly."},{"lineNumber":19983,"originalJapaneseLine":"「さ、酒に……うっぷ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The booze... ugh."},{"lineNumber":19984,"originalJapaneseLine":"　付き合ってやった、だけどぅわぁ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"I just kept you company, but... ugh...\""},

{"lineNumber":19985,"originalJapaneseLine":"それだけ言って、ランスは倒れた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Having said that, Lance collapsed."},

{"lineNumber":19986,"originalJapaneseLine":"「恥さらしめが…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What a disgrace...\" "},

{"lineNumber":19987,"originalJapaneseLine":"翌日。","translatedEnglishLine":"The next day."},

{"lineNumber":19988,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あーくそ……頭がガンガンする……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah damn... my head is pounding...\" "},

{"lineNumber":19989,"originalJapaneseLine":"「大丈夫ですか、ランス様……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Are you alright, Lord Lance..."},

{"lineNumber":19990,"originalJapaneseLine":"　お水、飲みます？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Would you like some water?\""}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ばかやろーーーーーーおおお！！！！
そんなこつぉ、さしぇるかーーーーー！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I won't let you do something like that!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぶっころおおおおおおぉぉす！！」
ランスはやおら剣を抜いて、
いいぞーーーー！　やれやれーーー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's the spirit! Keep it up!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは剣を手にぶら下げたまま、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance, still holding his sword loosely,
"Alright, alright, here you go, here you go!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どんどんいきましょーーーー」
好きだーーーーーーーーー！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I love herーーーーーー！！

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラヴーーーーーーーーー！！」
「むう……なかなかはっきり物を言うじゃないか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm... you speak quite clearly after all...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 総統閣下ならそれ以上でしょう！　でしょう！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If it's the Commander, it must be even more so! Right!?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あたりまえだろーーーーー！
俺様は……総統様だぞーーーー！」
すぅっ、とランスは大きく息を吸った。
シベリアより冷たい視線に気づいた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He noticed a gaze colder than Siberia.
"What's wrong? Go ahead and say it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この醜態、全て包み隠さず
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: All of this disgrace, without hiding a thing,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リセットに伝えるからのう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I'll tell Reset everything, you know."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おりょーん？　どうしたんですか、閣下！
気にせずズバーっといきましょうよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Don't worry, just go ahead and say it clearly!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビヨンホウはズバーッと斬られた。
付き合ってやった、だけどぅわぁ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I just kept you company, but... ugh..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それだけ言って、ランスは倒れた。
「あーくそ……頭がガンガンする……」

originalJapaneseLine.description: The original line in Japanese exactly as it was in the input

translatedEnglishLine.description: The original line translated to English
